- Changes in settings.py, styles directory, main.html, navbar.html (added logo), model.py(added featured img)

- pip3 install pillow (image processing library)

- url (added path to find locally uploaded images)

-forms.py (added enctype="multipart/form-data)

- views.py (added request.FILES)

- For production we can't have our static files on same server. So, we will use django collect static to collect alll the
  static files and create a bundle, then djnago will handle rest of the stuff for us

    python manage.py collectstatic

- pip3 install whitenoise (A solution to handle static files in production) and add it to middleware in settings.py